    dc:description "FIGURES 41 – 47. Cladiopsocus mocoaensis n. sp. Male. 41. Forewing. 42. Hindwing. 43. Front view of head. 44. Epiproct. 45. Left paraproct. 46. Hypandrium. 47. Phallosome. Scales in mm." ;
